                <div>
                    <h5>
                        Training Experience
                    </h5>
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        Since 2018, I have been dedicated to training aspiring full stack developers, with over 400 students taught to date. My training approach emphasizes practical, hands-on learning, ensuring that students not only understand the theoretical aspects of development but also gain the skills needed to build real-world applications.
                        I'm proud to have mentored more than 20 of my students who have gone on to secure positions in various IT fields, contributing to the tech industry with the skills and knowledge they acquired under my guidance.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h5>
                        Team Leadership
                    </h5>
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        In addition to my role as a trainer, I have been working as a team leader since 2022, guiding development teams through complex projects from conception to deployment. My leadership style focuses on fostering collaboration, encouraging continuous learning, and ensuring that every team member contributes to the project's success. I excel at project management, task distribution, and problem-solving, which enables my teams to deliver high-quality software solutions on time and within scope.
                    </p>
